{"tid":1050069,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大麻其實有好處","createTime":"2019-03-06T17:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T02:20:02.000Z","uid":221100,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4c2ff53418bbc38ceb0c5e3533654379eeb5bec0","tid":1050069,"uid":221100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T17:39:29.000Z","msg":"英國一名81歲肺癌患者拒絕化療，自行服用「大麻油」兩個月後，X光片顯示其腫瘤明顯縮細，引起關注，醫生在期刊報告他的病例。不過本港有醫生提醒，有藥用價值的只是大麻提煉出來、不會導致人感興奮的成份「大麻二酚」（cannabidiol，CBD），而非大麻煙；醫學界至今仍未就「大麻二酚」治療癌症作大規模臨床研究，不能以單一案件作定案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190307&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59335542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190307%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59335542&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QIpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=898c37b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190307%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59335542&h=19a0ab69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190307&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59335542</a>"},{"pid":"88a9bdba3024a37b9afed9a6274ba3acf8dfd6b6","tid":1050069,"uid":84212,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T17:42:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"876381bd8ba8e4a4a2f760ffabd942893e89576d","tid":1050069,"uid":221100,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"88a9bdba3024a37b9afed9a6274ba3acf8dfd6b6","tid":1050069,"uid":84212,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T17:42:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T17:43:31.000Z","msg":"吊，醫學報告，關我咩事"},{"pid":"25b2ad881e141a943e0673cda46acf81ae59ff6d","tid":1050069,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:01:45.000Z","msg":"大麻=毒品=害人<br />\n食大麻醫病=籍口=吸毒<br />\n吸毒=社會垃圾=犯罪=唔死都無撚用"},{"pid":"b58789b61203073cd7837e52c3c05e2e3b3ff5d5","tid":1050069,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:05:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c41418ed26824e9179f0a797749e2483aaee68a","tid":1050069,"uid":229834,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"25b2ad881e141a943e0673cda46acf81ae59ff6d","tid":1050069,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:01:45.000Z","msg":"大麻=毒品=害人<br />\n食大麻醫病=籍口=吸毒<br />\n吸毒=社會垃圾=犯罪=唔死都無撚用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:27:43.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n<br />\n俾你個滑坡跣到攤攤腰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔見筆 = 死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PYKZLcc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPYKZLcc.png&h=e5db218b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d014a549ea66faafa7f4f127eb1c31c1bb785017","tid":1050069,"uid":61506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:30:40.000Z","msg":"醫學用大麻同娛樂用大麻點同"},{"pid":"b0be8173f61f680ca5939f536727e10bcc802659","tid":1050069,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d014a549ea66faafa7f4f127eb1c31c1bb785017","tid":1050069,"uid":61506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:30:40.000Z","msg":"醫學用大麻同娛樂用大麻點同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:31:51.000Z","msg":"大麻撚: 你唔好理"},{"pid":"9de9867cae498e6abe4251b24cc8c0fea89ff156","tid":1050069,"uid":61174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:57:09.000Z","msg":"CBD油來㗎喎關大麻咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁想啪CBD去鴻福堂日日買枝火麻仁來隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/full/10.1177/2050313X19832160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1177%2F2050313X19832160&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QIpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=04ca3e1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/full/10.1177/2050313X19832160</a><br />\n<br />\nOn further questioning, the patient stated that he had started taking CBD (&ldquo;MyCBD&rdquo;) oil 2% (200&thinsp;mg CBD in 10&thinsp;mL) from the beginning of September 2017. He took two drops (0.06&thinsp;mL, 1.32&thinsp;mg CBD) twice daily for a week and then nine drops (0.3&thinsp;mL, 6&thinsp;mg CBD) twice daily until the end of September. Following the November 2017 CT scan, the patient started taking nine drops twice daily but had to stop around a week later."},{"pid":"2a38dc2affcfdc3ea56772ab579f15957a7d6a49","tid":1050069,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9de9867cae498e6abe4251b24cc8c0fea89ff156","tid":1050069,"uid":61174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T19:57:09.000Z","msg":"CBD油來㗎喎關大麻咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁想啪CBD去鴻福堂日日買枝火麻仁來隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/full/10.1177/2050313X19832160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1177%2F2050313X19832160&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QIpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=04ca3e1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/full/10.1177/2050313X19832160</a><br />\n<br />\nOn further questioning, the patient stated that he had started taking CBD (&ldquo;MyCBD&rdquo;) oil 2% (200&thinsp;mg CBD in 10&thinsp;mL) from the beginning of September 2017. He took two drops (0.06&thinsp;mL, 1.32&thinsp;mg CBD) twice daily for a week and then nine drops (0.3&thinsp;mL, 6&thinsp;mg CBD) twice daily until the end of September. Following the November 2017 CT scan, the patient started taking nine drops twice daily but had to stop around a week later."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:21:03.000Z","msg":"道友最鍾意作嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609dc85df84d571055460d09de482a1ea6455b96","tid":1050069,"uid":199787,"like"